      | AD_User_ID.Identifier | Name     | OPT.EMail          | OPT.Login |
      | testUser_1            | testUser | testUser@email.com | testUser  |
    And load AD_Roles
      | AD_Role_ID.Identifier | Name  |
      | userRole              | WebUI |
